ISLAMABAD, May 19 (APP):President Dr Arif Alvi Friday condemned the suicide attack on the convoy of Jamaat e Islami in Zhob.In a tweet, the President told that he called Amir Jamaat e Islami Sirajul Haq on telephone and inquired after his well being.
The President said during the conversation he expressed best wishes for Sirajul Haq and prayed for him.He also prayed for early recovery of the injured.
